Bella Baby Cotton Buds A200 (Pack of 200) Price: Rs.79

Natural products are always best for the human skin
column13:
especially the ones that are used on an infant’s delicate skin. Like all the other cotton products from Bella Baby the Cotton Buds are also made of 100 per cent natural cotton. These absolutely hygienic cotton swabs are tested and proven to have no allergenic properties.\xa0

The Cotton Buds from Bella Baby can be used for cleansing and make-up purposes. You can use these soft Cotton Swabs to gently clean your infant’s ears and to dry their navels after their bath. The pliable plastic stem makes them easy to use and the flexibility gives you more options of use. You can use these Cotton Buds to apply and even perfect your make-up. They come with a plastic cover that will allow you to easy store them in the bathrooms without getting wet or dirty. These plastic bags are made with a very convenient size that will easily fit into your vanity bags and thus allow you to carry them around and be of use to you anytime anywhere.

Bella Baby Cotton Buds A100 (Pack of 100) Price: Rs.45

Cotton swabs are mainly used to clean or scratch the ear canal. When used for this purpose it is mandatory that the cotton used on the swab is clean and made of skin friendly cotton fibres. If the cotton fibres are skin irritant then it can cause skin irritations and infections. The Bella Cotton Buds are made of 100 per cent cotton. These are highly hygienic and is suitable for the entire family. You can be absolutely sure of using these cotton swabs on your infant's skin and even on your sensitive skin to apply or remove make-up. Since these Bella Cotton Swabs come in a plastic bag they will conveniently fit into your vanity bags. Always make sure your children use cotton swabs and other similar products only under your strict supervision
